Seto is represented by Ken-On. ==Biography== On 2013 Seto was part of Ken-On's Next Generation and on 2014 he debuted in the drama Yowakutemo Katemasu. His film debut was in Strayer's Chronicle on 2015. Later on August of the same year Seto is now affiliated with Ken-On.
